{
  "stem": "979.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They says, because the-- the England-- I mean Germany started the war with-- with-- with Britain and, you know, the Americans, too.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they-- they came here right away-- I mean-- I mean in Greece right away.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And within three days-- and everything changed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was the beginning for the Jews-- for the beginning of the end.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we still were not aware, because they-- they didn't bother us for a year.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They-- they didn't know who was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Germans didn't know?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we thought, oh, they're-- we're-- they're not doing anything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't know what went on in Europe.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So one day--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, as far as I know, even my family didn't know what's gonna happen.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We heard that there's a war.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we didn't know what they're gonna do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That we didn't-- we didn't know they were such cruel people like that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We never even dream of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when they came-- when they came to Greece, we were very-- we were doing normal-- we having normal life.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And since we were all musicians, even me-- oh-- I have to go a bit backwards.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "See-- Fine",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--when we were in Greece, my father, my-- my sister, and brother were very good pianists.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They already had started since they were very young.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And especially my brother had special talent.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they went to the music school in Greece.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the teacher was one very famous teacher.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Although he was Greek, but he grew up in-- you know, where Mozart was born-- Salsburg, I think it is.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He grew up in Salsburg.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He grew up there, and he was a-- a prodigy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he became a teacher.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then he came to Greece to teach Greek children.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
